Patient
│
├── Encounter (linked via patient_id)
│   ├── Condition (linked via encounter_id & patient_id)
│   ├── Observation (linked via encounter_id & patient_id)
│   ├── Procedure (linked via encounter_id & patient_id)
│   └── MedicationRequest (linked via encounter_id & patient_id)
│
├── CarePlan (linked via patient_id)
│
└── ClinicalNote (flexible links to Encounter, Condition, etc.)